<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>苡焄｜飲食初步分析報告</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --sage: #8B9E7E;
    --sage-light: #C5D4BD;
    --sage-pale: #EEF3EB;
    --terra: #C17F59;
    --terra-light: #E8C4A8;
    --terra-pale: #F9F0E8;
    --cream: #FDFBF7;
    --bark: #3D3229;
    --bark-light: #6B5A4E;
    --warn: #C17F59;
    --warn-bg: #FEF3EB;
    --ok: #8B9E7E;
    --ok-bg: #EEF3EB;
    --info: #6B8CAE;
    --info-bg: #EAF1F8;
    --danger: #C0614A;
    --danger-bg: #FBF0EE;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--bark);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* HEADER */
  .header {
    background: var(--bark);
    color: var(--cream);
    padding: 48px 40px 36px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -60px; right: -60px;
    width: 280px; height: 280px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(139,158,126,0.15);
  }
  .header::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -40px; left: 120px;
    width: 180px; height: 180px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(193,127,89,0.12);
  }
  .header-eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--sage-light);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .header-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }
  .header-sub {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(253,251,247,0.6);
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }
  .header-date {
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(253,251,247,0.45);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    padding-top: 16px;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }

  /* CONTAINER */
  .container { max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 24px 80px; }

  /* SECTION LABEL */
  .section-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    padding-left: 2px;
  }

  /* PROFILE CARDS */
  .profile-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .profile-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid rgba(139,158,126,0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px;
  }
  .profile-card-label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--bark-light); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .profile-card-value { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--bark); }
  .profile-card-value span { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--bark-light); }
  .profile-card-sub { font-size: 11px; color: var(--sage); margin-top: 2px; }

  .tdee-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .tdee-card {
    background: var(--sage-pale);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(139,158,126,0.25);
  }
  .tdee-card-label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--bark-light); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .tdee-card-value { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--sage); }
  .tdee-card-value span { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--bark-light); }
  .tdee-card-sub { font-size: 11px; color: var(--bark-light); margin-top: 2px; }

  /* DAY CARD */
  .day-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid rgba(61,50,41,0.1);
    border-radius: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .day-card-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 18px 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(61,50,41,0.07);
  }
  .day-card-date { font-size: 12px; color: var(--bark-light); margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .day-card-kcal { font-size: 19px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--bark); }
  .badge {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 5px 14px;
    border-radius: 99px;
  }
  .badge-ok { background: var(--ok-bg); color: #4A6B3D; }
  .badge-low { background: var(--info-bg); color: #3A5F82; }
  .badge-warn { background: var(--warn-bg); color: #8B4A1E; }
  .badge-danger { background: var(--danger-bg); color: #7A3020; }

  /* MEALS */
  .meals { padding: 0 24px; }
  .meal-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 11px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(61,50,41,0.06);
    font-size: 13.5px;
  }
  .meal-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .meal-time { color: var(--terra); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; width: 42px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .meal-desc { flex: 1; color: var(--bark-light); line-height: 1.5; }
  .meal-kcal { font-weight: 700; color: var(--bark); white-space: nowrap; font-size: 13px; }

  /* MACRO BARS */
  .macro-section { padding: 16px 24px; background: var(--cream); border-top: 1px solid rgba(61,50,41,0.06); }
  .macro-title { font-size: 11px; color: var(--bark-light); margin-bottom: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
  .macro-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 7px; }
  .macro-label { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--bark-light); width: 32px; }
  .macro-bar-bg { flex: 1; height: 8px; background: rgba(61,50,41,0.08); border-radius: 99px; overflow: hidden; }
  .macro-bar-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 99px; transition: width 0.6s ease; }
  .fill-protein { background: var(--sage); }
  .fill-carb { background: var(--terra); }
  .fill-fat { background: #A89080; }
  .macro-val { font-size: 12px; color: var(--bark-light); width: 80px; text-align: right; }

  /* FLAGS */
  .flags { padding: 14px 24px 18px; background: #fff; border-top: 1px solid rgba(61,50,41,0.06); }
  .flag-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: var(--bark-light);
    margin-bottom: 5px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .flag-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .flag-dot { width: 16px; height: 16px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; }
  .dot-warn { background: var(--terra); }
  .dot-ok { background: var(--sage); }
  .dot-info { background: var(--info); }

  /* ACTIVITY CHIPS */
  .activity-row {
    padding: 12px 24px;
    background: var(--cream);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(61,50,41,0.06);
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .activity-label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--bark-light); margin-right: 2px; }
  .chip {
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 99px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(61,50,41,0.12);
    color: var(--bark-light);
    background: #fff;
  }
  .chip-warn { background: var(--warn-bg); color: #8B4A1E; border-color: var(--terra-light); }

  /* SUMMARY */
  .summary-card {
    background: var(--bark);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 28px 28px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--cream);
  }
  .summary-card-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .summary-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 11px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(253,251,247,0.1);
    font-size: 13px;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .summary-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .summary-key { color: rgba(253,251,247,0.55); flex-shrink: 0; }
  .summary-val { text-align: right; font-weight: 500; }
  .val-concern { color: var(--terra-light); }
  .val-ok { color: var(--sage-light); }

  /* KEY INSIGHTS */
  .insights-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .insight-card {
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 18px;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
  }
  .insight-card.concern { background: var(--danger-bg); border-color: rgba(192,97,74,0.2); }
  .insight-card.warn { background: var(--warn-bg); border-color: rgba(193,127,89,0.25); }
  .insight-card.info { background: var(--info-bg); border-color: rgba(107,140,174,0.2); }
  .insight-num { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .concern .insight-num { color: var(--danger); }
  .warn .insight-num { color: var(--warn); }
  .info .insight-num { color: var(--info); }
  .insight-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--bark); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .insight-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--bark-light); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* FOOTER */
  .footer {
    margin-top: 48px;
    padding-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(61,50,41,0.12);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--bark-light);
    text-align: center;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  /* DIVIDER */
  .section-divider { margin: 32px 0 20px; }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .profile-grid, .tdee-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .insights-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .header { padding: 32px 20px 24px; }
    .container { padding: 24px 16px 60px; }
    .day-card-header { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 8px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
  <div class="header-eyebrow">Abby Eat Life｜營養諮詢</div>
  <div class="header-title">苡焄的飲食初步分析</div>
  <div class="header-sub">首次諮詢｜飲食紀錄檢視 × 減脂目標規劃</div>
  <div class="header-date">分析日期：2026 年 4 月 2 日｜資料區間：2026/3/27 – 4/1</div>
</div>

<div class="container">

  <!-- 基本資料 -->
  <div class="section-label">基本資料</div>
  <div class="profile-grid">
    <div class="profile-card">
      <div class="profile-card-label">身高</div>
      <div class="profile-card-value">168<span> cm</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="profile-card">
      <div class="profile-card-label">體重</div>
      <div class="profile-card-value">63<span> kg</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="profile-card">
      <div class="profile-card-label">腰圍</div>
      <div class="profile-card-value">75<span> cm</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="profile-card">
      <div class="profile-card-label">目標體重</div>
      <div class="profile-card-value">~55<span> kg</span></div>
      <div class="profile-card-sub">差距約 8 kg</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="tdee-grid">
    <div class="tdee-card">
      <div class="tdee-card-label">BMI</div>
      <div class="tdee-card-value">22.3<span></span></div>
      <div class="tdee-card-sub">正常範圍</div>
    </div>
    <div class="tdee-card">
      <div class="tdee-card-label">估算 TDEE</div>
      <div class="tdee-card-value">1,750<span> kcal</span></div>
      <div class="tdee-card-sub">低活動量係數 ×1.2</div>
    </div>
    <div class="tdee-card">
      <div class="tdee-card-label">減脂目標熱量</div>
      <div class="tdee-card-value">1,350–1,400<span> kcal</span></div>
      <div class="tdee-card-sub">赤字約 350 kcal</div>
    </div>
    <div class="tdee-card">
      <div class="tdee-card-label">蛋白質目標</div>
      <div class="tdee-card-value">95<span> g</span></div>
      <div class="tdee-card-sub">1.5 g/kg 體重</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 三大關鍵問題 -->
  <div class="section-label">本週三大問題</div>
  <div class="insights-grid">
    <div class="insight-card concern">
      <div class="insight-num">40–65%</div>
      <div class="insight-title">蛋白質嚴重不足</div>
      <div class="insight-desc">每天蛋白質平均只達目標的一半，長期下來減脂同時會流失肌肉，讓代謝越來越低。</div>
    </div>
    <div class="insight-card warn">
      <div class="insight-num">×2.3</div>
      <div class="insight-title">週末大吃是平日的兩倍</div>
      <div class="insight-desc">平日壓低熱量 → 聚餐日爆破的循環，身體在低熱量日降低代謝、高熱量日全囤積。</div>
    </div>
    <div class="insight-card info">
      <div class="insight-num">350–7939</div>
      <div class="insight-title">步數極度不穩定</div>
      <div class="insight-desc">本週步數落差超過 20 倍，活動量無法累積，是TDEE偏低的主要原因。</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 每日飲食 -->
  <div class="section-divider"></div>
  <div class="section-label">每日飲食分析</div>

  <!-- 3/27 -->
  <div class="day-card">
    <div class="day-card-header">
      <div>
        <div class="day-card-date">2026 / 3 / 27（週五）</div>
        <div class="day-card-kcal">攝取約 1,480 kcal</div>
      </div>
      <span class="badge badge-ok">熱量尚可</span>
    </div>
    <div class="meals">
      <div class="meal-row">
        <span class="meal-time">7:30</span>
        <span class="meal-desc">白飯一碗 + 煎香腸兩根 + 豬肉味噌湯一碗</span>
        <span class="meal-kcal">~620 kcal</span>
      </div>
      <div class="meal-row">
        <span class="meal-time">13:31</span>
        <span class="meal-desc">咖哩雞套餐（白飯、煎蛋、沙拉、清湯）+ 椰奶西米露</span>
        <span class="meal-kcal">~670 kcal</span>
      </div>
      <div class="meal-row">
        <span class="meal-time">21:00</span>
        <span class="meal-desc">Pretz 兩包 + 梅子四顆</span>
        <span class="meal-kcal">~190 kcal</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="macro-section">
      <div class="macro-title">營養素分布（目標：蛋白質 95g）</div>
      <div class="macro-row">
        <span class="macro-label">蛋白</span>
        <div class="macro-bar-bg"><div class="macro-bar-fill fill-protein" style="width:58%"></div></div>
        <span class="macro-val">約 55g / 95g</span>
      </div>
      <div class="macro-row">
        <span class="macro-label">碳水</span>
        <div class="macro-bar-bg"><div class="macro-bar-fill fill-carb" style="width:78%"></div></div>
        <span class="macro-val">約 210g</span>
      </div>
      <div class="macro-row">
        <span class="macro-label">脂肪</span>
        <div class="macro-bar-bg"><div class="macro-bar-fill fill-fat" style="width:55%"></div></div>
        <span class="macro-val">約 38g</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flags">
      <div class="flag-item"><div class="flag-dot dot-warn">▲</div>香腸是加工肉品，鈉高、脂肪高，建議換成雞胸或水煮蛋</div>
      <div class="flag-item"><div class="flag-dot dot-warn">▲</div>晚上宵夜（Pretz + 梅子）：熱量 190 kcal 但蛋白質幾乎為零，是精緻零食</div>
      <div class="flag-item"><div class="flag-dot dot-info">●</div>蛋白質只達目標的 58%，這天飲食結構還算規律，是最容易調整的基礎</div>
    </div>
    <div class="activity-row">
      <span class="activity-label">活動：</span>
      <span class="chip">步數 1,414</span>
      <span class="chip chip-warn">久坐日</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 3/29 -->
  <div class="day-card">
    <div class="day-card-header">
      <div>
        <div class="day-card-date">2026 / 3 / 29（週日）</div>
        <div class="day-card-kcal">攝取約 1,120 kcal</div>
      </div>
      <span class="badge badge-low">熱量偏低</span>
    </div>
    <div class="meals">
      <div class="meal-row">
        <span class="meal-time">11:52</span>
        <span class="meal-desc">菠菜咖哩雞 + 起司印度烤餅半張 + 印度奶茶 300ml + 印度烤雞一塊</span>
        <span class="meal-kcal">~720 kcal</span>
      </div>
      <div class="meal-row">
        <span class="meal-time">20:00</span>
        <span class="meal-desc">印度烤雞一塊 + 起司印度烤餅半張</span>
        <span class="meal-kcal">~400 kcal</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="macro-section">
      <div class="macro-title">營養素分布（目標：蛋白質 95g）</div>
      <div class="macro-row">
        <span class="macro-label">蛋白</span>
        <div class="macro-bar-bg"><div class="macro-bar-fill fill-protein" style="width:65%"></div></div>
        <span class="macro-val">約 62g / 95g</span>
      </div>
      <div class="macro-row">
        <span class="macro-label">碳水</span>
        <div class="macro-bar-bg"><div class="macro-bar-fill fill-carb" style="width:45%"></div></div>
        <span class="macro-val">約 115g</span>
      </div>
      <div class="macro-row">
        <span class="macro-label">脂肪</span>
        <div class="macro-bar-bg"><div class="macro-bar-fill fill-fat" style="width:48%"></div></div>
        <span class="macro-val">約 35g</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flags">
      <div class="flag-item"><div class="flag-dot dot-ok">✓</div>兩餐都有蛋白質來源（烤雞），是本週飲食結構最好的一天</div>
      <div class="flag-item"><div class="flag-dot dot-warn">▲</div>印度奶茶含糖量不明，估計 150–250 kcal，建議改無糖或減糖</div>
      <div class="flag-item"><div class="flag-dot dot-warn">▲</div>只吃兩餐、熱量明顯不足，容易讓身體降低代謝，也容易下一餐補償性暴食</div>
    </div>
    <div class="activity-row">
      <span class="activity-label">活動：</span>
      <span class="chip">步數 350</span>
      <span class="chip chip-warn">近乎靜止</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 3/31 -->
  <div class="day-card">
    <div class="day-card-header">
      <div>
        <div class="day-card-date">2026 / 3 / 31（週二）</div>
        <div class="day-card-kcal">攝取約 2,800–3,200 kcal</div>
      </div>
      <span class="badge badge-danger">大幅超標</span>
    </div>
    <div class="meals">
      <div class="meal-row">
        <span class="meal-time">12:15</span>
        <span class="meal-desc">咖哩雞便當（飯、麵、醃漬物）+ 草莓泡芙 + 星冰樂</span>
        <span class="meal-kcal">~1,050 kcal</span>
      </div>
      <div class="meal-row">
        <span class="meal-time">15:35</span>
        <span class="meal-desc">牛乳 200ml</span>
        <span class="meal-kcal">~130 kcal</span>
      </div>
      <div class="meal-row">
        <span class="meal-time">17:00</span>
        <span class="meal-desc">韓國烤肉 + 青菜 + 瑪格麗酒 200ml + 汽水 300ml<br>韓式煎餅 4 塊 + 炒年糕一碗 + 炸雞三塊（含起司炸雞兩塊）</span>
        <span class="meal-kcal">~1,650 kcal</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="macro-section">
      <div class="macro-title">營養素分布（目標：蛋白質 95g）</div>
      <div class="macro-row">
        <span class="macro-label">蛋白</span>
